
		        Login.app
	
			Per Liden
		    (per@rsn.hk-r.se)


Description
--------------------------------------------------------------
Login.app will give you a nice looking login interface to 
Linux/Unix. It is running under X. This is NOT a hack of xdm. 
It is developed, and so far only tested, under Linux.


